    "body": "Summary\n- Add loop_layout to T.Parallel and document constraints/rationale\n- Enforce outermost annotation semantics across validator/lowering\n- Adopt annotated loop layout (and predicate) when present in annotations\n- Fuse parallel loops: reshape Fragment to fused 1D via Fragment::Reshape\n- Lower: strip parallel_loop_layout/predicate annotations in LowerParallelLoop\n- Tests: add lazy_jit tests for loop layout codegen (CUDA); remove old debug script\n- Docs: update control_flow guide for loop_layout\n\nWhy\n- Inner loops cannot govern outer loops; outermost loop is the right scope to manage and transform the entire nested region\n- Reshape on fuse produces correct, simplified 1D layout and avoids hand-crafted index/thread expressions\n- Removing annotations at lower prevents complex payloads from leaking into later passes that do not visit annotation bodies\n\nKey Files\n- tilelang/language/loop.py: add loop_layout param; docstring notes + rationale\n- docs/programming_guides/control_flow.md: loop_layout attached to outermost loop\n- src/ir.cc: only outermost parallel loop carries annotations (with rationale)\n- src/transform/parallel_loop_layout_validator.h: validate outermost annotation; rationale comment\n- src/transform/layout_inference.cc: attach inferred loop layout/predicate on outermost loop\n- src/op/parallel.h/.cc: cache annotated layout/predicate; adopt in InferLayout; infer-only flag\n- src/transform/common/loop_fusion_utils.h: reshape layout on fuse; drop mismatched annotation\n- src/transform/loop_partition.cc: strip layout/predicate annotations in LowerParallelLoop\n- testing/python/layout/test_parallel_loop_layout.py: new lazy_jit tests\n\nValidation\n- CUDA codegen asserts pass in new tests under testing/python/layout\n\n<!-- This is an auto-generated comment: release notes by coderabbit.ai -->\n## Summary by CodeRabbit\n\n* **Documentation**\n  * Clarified parallel-loop guidance and expanded optional hints; documented that layout annotations attach to the outermost parallel loop and added loop_layout usage guidance.\n\n* **New Features**\n  * Added loop_layout keyword to parallel constructs and copy APIs to provide an optional thread/layout hint for vectorization.\n\n* **Bug Fixes**\n  * Ensure layout annotations and coalescing hints apply only to the outermost parallel loop and strip stale annotations; copy validates compatible patterns when loop_layout is used.\n\n* **Tests**\n  * Added tests validating parallel loop layout handling and vectorized copy generation.\n\n<sub>✏️ Tip: You can customize this high-level summary in your review settings.</sub>\n<!-- end of auto-generated comment: release notes by coderabbit.ai -->",
